            "id": "devotion",
            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EPaul%20shows%20us%20that%20we%20are%20a%20totally%20interrelated%20body%2C%20not%20just%20independent%20parts%20thrown%20together.%20No%20part%20of%20the%20human%20body%20can%20continue%20to%20function%20normally%20when%20one%20part%20is%20in%20pain.%20The%20whole%20body%20focuses%20its%20attention%20on%20the%20area%20afflicted.%20In%20the%20same%20way%2C%20Mordecai%20sent%20word%20to%20Esther%20not%20to%20think%20that%20just%20because%20she%20lived%20in%20the%20palace%20she%20would%20escape%20the%20sentence%20of%20death%20imposed%20on%20the%20Jews%20(Esther%204%3A13).%20If%20she%20did%20not%20help%2C%20she%20would%20be%20destroyed%2C%20too.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EOur%20influences%20and%20gifts%20are%20given%20to%20us%20by%20God%20to%20help%20others%20for%20%22such%20a%20time%20as%20this%22%20(Esther%204%3A14).%20Let%20us%20take%20inventory%20of%20the%20positions%2C%20finances%2C%20and%20grace%20of%20God%20in%20our%20lives%20and%20see%20whom%20those%20gifts%20were%20intended%20to%20help.%20If%20we%20keep%20them%20for%20ourselves%20and%20do%20not%20identify%20with%20those%20in%20need%2C%20we%20will%20cry%20for%20help%20one%20day%20and%20no%20one%20will%20respond.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EBecause%20Esther%20was%20obedient%2C%20the%20words%20of%20David's%20psalm%20came%20true%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Haman%3A%20%22Look!%20They%20have%20fallen!%20They%20have%20been%20thrown%20down%2C%20never%20to%20rise%20again%22%20(Psalm%2036%3A12).%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
        {
            "id": "ot-passage",
            "type": "passage",
            "title": "Old Testament Reading",
            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Esther.4:1-7:10",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EEsther%204%3A1-7%3A10%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_4_1%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EEsther%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EMordecai%20Requests%20Esther%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Help%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20Mordecai%20learned%20about%20all%20that%20had%20been%20done%2C%20he%20tore%20his%20clothes%2C%20put%20on%20burlap%20and%20ashes%2C%20and%20went%20out%20into%20the%20city%2C%20crying%20with%20a%20loud%20and%20bitter%20wail.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_4_2%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20went%20as%20far%20as%20the%20gate%20of%20the%20palace%2C%20for%20no%20one%20was%20allowed%20to%20enter%20the%20palace%20gate%20while%20wearing%20clothes%20of%20mourning.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_4_3%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20as%20news%20of%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20decree%20reached%20all%20the%20provinces%2C%20there%20was%20great%20mourning%20among%20the%20Jews.%20They%20fasted%2C%20wept%2C%20and%20wailed%2C%20and%20many%20people%20lay%20in%20burlap%20and%20ashes.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_4_4%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20Queen%20Esther%26%23x2019%3Bs%20maids%20and%20eunuchs%20came%20and%20told%20her%20about%20Mordecai%2C%20she%20was%20deeply%20distressed.%20She%20sent%20clothing%20to%20him%20to%20replace%20the%20burlap%2C%20but%20he%20refused%20it.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_4_5%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Esther%20sent%20for%20Hathach%2C%20one%20of%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20eunuchs%20who%20had%20been%20appointed%20as%20her%20attendant.%20She%20ordered%20him%20to%20go%20to%20Mordecai%20and%20find%20out%20what%20was%20troubling%20him%20and%20why%20he%20was%20in%20mourning.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_4_6%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20Hathach%20went%20out%20to%20Mordecai%20in%20the%20square%20in%20front%20of%20the%20palace%20gate.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_4_7%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EMordecai%20told%20him%20the%20whole%20story%2C%20including%20the%20exact%20amount%20of%20money%20Haman%20had%20promised%20to%20pay%20into%20the%20royal%20treasury%20for%20the%20destruction%20of%20the%20Jews.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_4_8%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EMordecai%20gave%20Hathach%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20decree%20issued%20in%20Susa%20that%20called%20for%20the%20death%20of%20all%20Jews.%20He%20asked%20Hathach%20to%20show%20it%20to%20Esther%20and%20explain%20the%20situation%20to%20her.%20He%20also%20asked%20Hathach%20to%20direct%20her%20to%20go%20to%20the%20king%20to%20beg%20for%20mercy%20and%20plead%20for%20her%20people.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_4_9%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20Hathach%20returned%20to%20Esther%20with%20Mordecai%26%23x2019%3Bs%20message.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_4_10%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Esther%20told%20Hathach%20to%20go%20back%20and%20relay%20this%20message%20to%20Mordecai%3A%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_4_11%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BAll%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20officials%20and%20even%20the%20people%20in%20the%20provinces%20know%20that%20anyone%20who%20appears%20before%20the%20king%20in%20his%20inner%20court%20without%20being%20invited%20is%20doomed%20to%20die%20unless%20the%20king%20holds%20out%20his%20gold%20scepter.%20And%20the%20king%20has%20not%20called%20for%20me%20to%20come%20to%20him%20for%20thirty%20days.%26%23x201D%3B%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_4_12%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20Hathach%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E4%3A12%3C%2Fspan%3E%20As%20in%20Greek%20version%3B%20Hebrew%20reads%20%3Cem%3Ethey.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20gave%20Esther%26%23x2019%3Bs%20message%20to%20Mordecai.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_4_13%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EMordecai%20sent%20this%20reply%20to%20Esther%3A%20%26%23x201C%3BDon%26%23x2019%3Bt%20think%20for%20a%20moment%20that%20because%20you%26%23x2019%3Bre%20in%20the%20palace%20you%20will%20escape%20when%20all%20other%20Jews%20are%20killed.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_4_14%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3EIf%20you%20keep%20quiet%20at%20a%20time%20like%20this%2C%20deliverance%20and%20relief%20for%20the%20Jews%20will%20arise%20from%20some%20other%20place%2C%20but%20you%20and%20your%20relatives%20will%20die.%20Who%20knows%20if%20perhaps%20you%20were%20made%20queen%20for%20just%20such%20a%20time%20as%20this%3F%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_4_15%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Esther%20sent%20this%20reply%20to%20Mordecai%3A%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_4_16%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BGo%20and%20gather%20together%20all%20the%20Jews%20of%20Susa%20and%20fast%20for%20me.%20Do%20not%20eat%20or%20drink%20for%20three%20days%2C%20night%20or%20day.%20My%20maids%20and%20I%20will%20do%20the%20same.%20And%20then%2C%20though%20it%20is%20against%20the%20law%2C%20I%20will%20go%20in%20to%20see%20the%20king.%20If%20I%20must%20die%2C%20I%20must%20die.%26%23x201D%3B%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_4_17%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20Mordecai%20went%20away%20and%20did%20everything%20as%20Esther%20had%20ordered%20him.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_5_1%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EEsther%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EEsther%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Request%20to%20the%20King%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EOn%20the%20third%20day%20of%20the%20fast%2C%20Esther%20put%20on%20her%20royal%20robes%20and%20entered%20the%20inner%20court%20of%20the%20palace%2C%20just%20across%20from%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20hall.%20The%20king%20was%20sitting%20on%20his%20royal%20throne%2C%20facing%20the%20entrance.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_5_2%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20he%20saw%20Queen%20Esther%20standing%20there%20in%20the%20inner%20court%2C%20he%20welcomed%20her%20and%20held%20out%20the%20gold%20scepter%20to%20her.%20So%20Esther%20approached%20and%20touched%20the%20end%20of%20the%20scepter.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_5_3%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20king%20asked%20her%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BWhat%20do%20you%20want%2C%20Queen%20Esther%3F%20What%20is%20your%20request%3F%20I%20will%20give%20it%20to%20you%2C%20even%20if%20it%20is%20half%20the%20kingdom!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_5_4%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20Esther%20replied%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BIf%20it%20please%20the%20king%2C%20let%20the%20king%20and%20Haman%20come%20today%20to%20a%20banquet%20I%20have%20prepared%20for%20the%20king.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_5_5%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20king%20turned%20to%20his%20attendants%20and%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BTell%20Haman%20to%20come%20quickly%20to%20a%20banquet%2C%20as%20Esther%20has%20requested.%26%23x201D%3B%20So%20the%20king%20and%20Haman%20went%20to%20Esther%26%23x2019%3Bs%20banquet.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_5_6%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20while%20they%20were%20drinking%20wine%2C%20the%20king%20said%20to%20Esther%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BNow%20tell%20me%20what%20you%20really%20want.%20What%20is%20your%20request%3F%20I%20will%20give%20it%20to%20you%2C%20even%20if%20it%20is%20half%20the%20kingdom!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_5_7%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EEsther%20replied%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BThis%20is%20my%20request%20and%20deepest%20wish.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_5_8%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EIf%20I%20have%20found%20favor%20with%20the%20king%2C%20and%20if%20it%20pleases%20the%20king%20to%20grant%20my%20request%20and%20do%20what%20I%20ask%2C%20please%20come%20with%20Haman%20tomorrow%20to%20the%20banquet%20I%20will%20prepare%20for%20you.%20Then%20I%20will%20explain%20what%20this%20is%20all%20about.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_5_9%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EHaman%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Plan%20to%20Kill%20Mordecai%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EHaman%20was%20a%20happy%20man%20as%20he%20left%20the%20banquet!%20But%20when%20he%20saw%20Mordecai%20sitting%20at%20the%20palace%20gate%2C%20not%20standing%20up%20or%20trembling%20nervously%20before%20him%2C%20Haman%20became%20furious.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_5_10%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EHowever%2C%20he%20restrained%20himself%20and%20went%20on%20home.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3EThen%20Haman%20gathered%20together%20his%20friends%20and%20Zeresh%2C%20his%20wife%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_5_11%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3Eand%20boasted%20to%20them%20about%